Craft Expertise			KEY:Craft Expertise ~ Dwarf Paragon				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary						SOURCEPAGE:p.35	DESC:A dwarf paragon may add his class level as a racial bonus on all Craft checks related to stone or metal items.		BONUS:VAR|DwarfCraftSkillBonus|DwarfParagonLVL
Improved Stonecunning		KEY:Improved Stonecunning ~ Dwarf Paragon			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary						SOURCEPAGE:p.35	DESC:At 1st level, a dwarf paragon's racial bonus on Search checks to notice unusual stonework increases to +4. The range at which he receives an automatic Search check for coming near an example of unusual stonework increases to 20 feet. Also, he can intuit where true north lies in relation to himself (as if he had 5 ranks in Survival) whenever underground.	BONUS:VAR|DwarfSearchSkillBonus|2
